  <h2>Where to add the rules</h2>

  <p>
    Custom rules are added in <code>/var/ossec/etc/rules/local_rules.xml</code>. After editing the file, restart the manager:
  </p>

  <pre style="background:#0f1419;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;overflow-x:auto;"><code style="color: #e5e7eb;">systemctl restart wazuh-manager</code></pre>

